---
import SectionLayout from "../layouts/SectionLayout.astro";
---

<SectionLayout title="My education">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mt-8">
    <div
      tabindex="0"
      id="platzi"
      class="collapse collapse-plus border border-emerald-300 bg-slave-100 rounded-box"
    >
      <div
        class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium font-roboto text-emerald-500"
      >
        Platzi
      </div>
      <div
        class="collapse-content flex flex-col gap-4 font-roboto text-slate-300"
      >
        <p>
          I have been a student of platzi since 2019. In platzi I have found
          many useful courses and a stuning comunity. I have learned from
          fullstack development to project managment. This are some of the
          courses I have took from them:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-4">
          <li>
            <a
              class="underline"
              id="managment"
              href="https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1721-gestion/diploma/detalle/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Fundamentals of project management</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="underline"
              id="javascript"
              href="https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1339-fundamentos-javascript/diploma/detalle/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Fundamentals of Javascript</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="underline"
              id="frontend"
              href="https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1640-course/diploma/detalle/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Frontend developer</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="underline"
              id="react"
              href="https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1651-react-ejs/diploma/detalle/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">React JS</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You can find more courses I have done <a
            class="underline"
            id="platzi_link"
            href="https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      tabindex="1"
      id="university"
      class="collapse collapse-plus border border-emerald-300 bg-slave-100 rounded-box"
    >
      <div
        class="collapse-title text-xl font-roboto font-medium text-emerald-500"
      >
        Univesidad de los Andes
      </div>
      <div
        class="collapse-content font-roboto text-slate-300 flex flex-col gap-4"
      >
        <p>
          I started my bachealors degree in Universidad de los Andes in the
          first semester of 2018. During my education I worked as a teaching
          assitant for the class Programaci√≥n Orientada a Objetos I
          (Object-oriented programming I) . This are some of the courses I took:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-4">
          <li>Object-oriented programming II</li>
          <li>Design and Analysis of Algorithms</li>
          <li>Probability and Statistics I</li>
          <li>Programming with Web Technologies</li>
          <li>Construction of Mobile Applications</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          For more information about Universidad de los Andes you can check its <a
            class="underline"
            id="QS"
            href="https://www.topuniversities.com/universities/universidad-de-los-andes"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">QS Ranking profile</a
          > which ranks it as the 5th best in LatAm.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script is:inline>
      const id_link = [
        {
          id: "managment",
          link: "https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1721-gestion/diploma/detalle/",
          section: "platzi",
        },
        {
          id: "javascript",
          link: "https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1339-fundamentos-javascript/diploma/detalle/",
          section: "platzi",
        },
        {
          id: "frontend",
          link: "https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1640-course/diploma/detalle/",
          section: "platzi",
        },
        {
          id: "react",
          link: "https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/curso/1651-react-ejs/diploma/detalle/",
          section: "platzi",
        },
        {
          id: "platzi_link",
          link: "https://platzi.com/p/santiagovargasvega/",
          section: "platzi",
        },
        {
          id: "QS",
          link: "https://www.topuniversities.com/universities/universidad-de-los-andes",
          section: "university",
        },
      ];
      id_link.map(({ id, section }) => {
        document.getElementById(id).addEventListener("mouseover", () => {
          const sectionHTML = document.getElementById(section);
          sectionHTML.classList.add("collapse-open");

          setTimeout(() => {
            sectionHTML.classList.remove("collapse-open");

            sectionHTML.focus();
          }, 1500);
        });
      });
    </script>
  </div>
</SectionLayout>
